1
00:01:44,680 --> 00:01:46,360
It's all over.

2
00:01:48,280 --> 00:01:49,400
I will protect you.

3
00:01:56,240 --> 00:01:57,080
Wait for me.

4
00:02:05,400 --> 00:02:06,560
Officer Zhuang.

5
00:02:08,400 --> 00:02:09,520
I plead guilty.

6
00:02:16,320 --> 00:02:18,440
I killed Mu Weijie.

7
00:02:24,720 --> 00:02:26,160
Is this world

8
00:02:27,040 --> 00:02:29,960
always black and white?

9
00:02:30,800 --> 00:02:34,120
Is a murderer always a bad person?

10
00:02:34,120 --> 00:02:36,680
Is a victim always a good person?

11
00:02:40,040 --> 00:02:41,520
You have no idea

12
00:02:41,520 --> 00:02:42,920
how much damage Mu Weijie

13
00:02:43,560 --> 00:02:46,960
has done to me.

14
00:02:48,760 --> 00:02:50,200
Do you know

15
00:02:50,800 --> 00:02:53,560
what chastity and self-esteem mean to a girl?

16
00:02:53,560 --> 00:02:56,079
How precious it is?

17
00:02:59,400 --> 00:03:01,920
Mu Weijie took nude photos of me.

18
00:03:01,920 --> 00:03:03,320
Faced with his threats

19
00:03:03,320 --> 00:03:05,240
and my mother's expectations,

20
00:03:05,920 --> 00:03:08,320
I had no choice but to submit to him.

21
00:03:10,440 --> 00:03:11,760
But I didn't expect

22
00:03:13,040 --> 00:03:16,079
that it would only make him worse

23
00:03:16,560 --> 00:03:19,000
and lead to a darker tomorrow.

24
00:03:24,720 --> 00:03:26,380
Mu Weijie, what are you doing?

25
00:03:26,480 --> 00:03:27,720
Mu Weijie!

26
00:03:28,760 --> 00:03:30,120
Let me go!

27
00:03:30,720 --> 00:03:32,640
He is an absolute monster.

28
00:03:34,480 --> 00:03:36,760
Not only did he satisfy his own lust,

29
00:03:37,720 --> 00:03:41,000
he also found thugs to humiliate me

30
00:03:41,880 --> 00:03:45,960
to stimulate his creative inspiration.

31
00:03:47,960 --> 00:03:48,760
Behave.

32
00:03:50,280 --> 00:03:51,120
Behave.

33
00:04:03,240 --> 00:04:04,400
Just like that,

34
00:04:05,120 --> 00:04:08,120
I became the Danaë in Mu Weijie's paintings.

35
00:04:08,600 --> 00:04:09,960
During those days,

36
00:04:10,280 --> 00:04:12,160
I lived in a daze,

37
00:04:12,560 --> 00:04:14,880
like a walking corpse.

38
00:04:15,440 --> 00:04:17,370
I hated myself for being like that,

39
00:04:17,720 --> 00:04:20,050
and I also hated the Danaë in the painting.

40
00:04:20,320 --> 00:04:21,360
I wanted

41
00:04:21,760 --> 00:04:24,440
to get rid of this demon with my own hands.

42
00:04:26,320 --> 00:04:27,320
When he died,

43
00:04:27,320 --> 00:04:29,760
I was actually very happy.

44
00:04:30,320 --> 00:04:32,560
Because I was finally free.

45
00:04:36,400 --> 00:04:37,800
I plead guilty.

46
00:04:44,640 --> 00:04:46,120
Please don't take her away.

47
00:04:46,120 --> 00:04:47,480
Wait a minute.

48
00:04:50,280 --> 00:04:51,440
Officer Zhuang.

49
00:04:53,640 --> 00:04:55,600
I need a favor from you.

50
00:04:58,159 --> 00:05:01,480
You must tell everyone the truth about this

51
00:05:01,480 --> 00:05:02,540
and make it public.

52
00:05:04,600 --> 00:05:06,200
I'm not afraid.

53
00:05:07,280 --> 00:05:09,400
We are the victims.

54
00:05:10,480 --> 00:05:12,240
If we don't speak up,

55
00:05:13,600 --> 00:05:18,240
thousands of monsters like Mu Weijie

56
00:05:18,240 --> 00:05:19,760
will get away with it.

57
00:05:21,000 --> 00:05:23,600
We won't be able to bear it.

58
00:05:25,360 --> 00:05:28,440
You must get justice for Rongrong

59
00:05:28,440 --> 00:05:30,120
and clear her name.

60
00:05:34,080 --> 00:05:35,080
I promise you.

61
00:06:02,360 --> 00:06:03,760
Based on what you went through,

62
00:06:03,760 --> 00:06:06,400
we have filed a public prosecution against Mu Weijie.

63
00:06:06,400 --> 00:06:07,800
After receiving the compensation,

64
00:06:07,800 --> 00:06:10,200
your mother will also be well taken care of.

65
00:06:10,400 --> 00:06:12,330
So you don't need to worry too much.

66
00:06:12,840 --> 00:06:13,560
Oh, right.

67
00:06:14,600 --> 00:06:16,200
As for the three men who assaulted you,

68
00:06:16,200 --> 00:06:18,240
we have already detained them.

69
00:06:21,280 --> 00:06:22,480
What about Rongrong?

70
00:06:22,880 --> 00:06:24,000
Is she okay?

71
00:06:25,120 --> 00:06:26,280
She's doing well.

72
00:06:26,520 --> 00:06:28,360
She has gone home to recuperate.

73
00:06:32,360 --> 00:06:33,890
Thank you, Officer Zhuang.

74
00:06:35,480 --> 00:06:37,880
There's one more question I want to ask you.

75
00:06:39,520 --> 00:06:41,320
How did you come up with

76
00:06:41,320 --> 00:06:43,400
such a method to kill someone?

77
00:06:46,760 --> 00:06:49,640
What makes you think I couldn't come up with it?

78
00:06:51,440 --> 00:06:52,840
With your life experience

79
00:06:52,840 --> 00:06:54,200
and at your age,

80
00:06:54,360 --> 00:06:56,159
you wouldn't have thought of it.

81
00:06:56,640 --> 00:06:57,520
Tell me,

82
00:06:57,840 --> 00:07:00,120
who helped you behind the scenes?

83
00:07:02,040 --> 00:07:04,400
Actually, I don't know who he is either.

84
00:07:05,280 --> 00:07:07,520
He contacted me first.

85
00:07:07,520 --> 00:07:09,680
As if telling a story,

86
00:07:10,040 --> 00:07:11,720
he told me the killing method

87
00:07:11,720 --> 00:07:13,120
and crime details.

88
00:07:13,360 --> 00:07:15,440
Very carefully.

89
00:07:16,440 --> 00:07:17,570
His profile picture

90
00:07:17,800 --> 00:07:18,920
is a lighthouse.

91
00:07:19,640 --> 00:07:23,280
The accident was the lighthouse's design.

92
00:07:43,120 --> 00:07:44,880
You handled this case beautifully.

93
00:07:44,880 --> 00:07:47,159
The Bureau is very satisfied with the efficiency

94
00:07:47,159 --> 00:07:48,800
of your accident investigation team.

95
00:07:48,800 --> 00:07:50,040
Keep up the good work.

96
00:07:56,840 --> 00:07:57,920
What's wrong?

97
00:07:59,280 --> 00:08:00,840
You guys are usually fooling around.

98
00:08:00,840 --> 00:08:02,360
You cracked the case today.

99
00:08:02,360 --> 00:08:04,040
Why the long faces?

100
00:08:06,440 --> 00:08:08,160
I just can't figure it out.

101
00:08:08,160 --> 00:08:10,880
Someone like Mu Weijie is rich

102
00:08:10,880 --> 00:08:12,540
and has both fame and fortune.

103
00:08:12,840 --> 00:08:15,640
How could he do such a heartless thing?

104
00:08:17,360 --> 00:08:18,690
I really can't imagine.

105
00:08:19,400 --> 00:08:22,440
If I were one of those girls,

106
00:08:23,360 --> 00:08:25,760
would I still have the courage to live on?

107
00:08:26,840 --> 00:08:27,760
I'm sorry.

108
00:08:29,520 --> 00:08:31,080
Whenever I think about these things,

109
00:08:31,080 --> 00:08:32,320
I just can't be happy.

110
00:08:33,799 --> 00:08:35,320
We are police officers.

111
00:08:35,880 --> 00:08:37,159
What you just mentioned,

112
00:08:37,159 --> 00:08:39,000
we've seen a lot over the years.

113
00:08:39,600 --> 00:08:41,520
For the horrible things they've suffered,

114
00:08:41,520 --> 00:08:43,520
someone has to be held accountable.

115
00:08:43,840 --> 00:08:45,640
You have already done very well.

116
00:08:45,880 --> 00:08:47,400
Don't be so down.

117
00:08:51,400 --> 00:08:52,640
Tell me, in this world,

118
00:08:52,640 --> 00:08:55,360
how many people are out there suffering?

119
00:08:56,160 --> 00:08:57,360
Why is it

120
00:08:57,360 --> 00:08:59,240
that they choose to use their own methods

121
00:08:59,240 --> 00:09:00,920
and refuse to trust us?

122
00:09:01,720 --> 00:09:02,880
In this case,

123
00:09:03,640 --> 00:09:05,560
what each girl goes through

124
00:09:05,920 --> 00:09:09,720
is a lifelong game of Russian roulette.

125
00:09:10,200 --> 00:09:12,920
They obviously did nothing wrong,

126
00:09:13,320 --> 00:09:16,520
yet they are threatened and persecuted.

127
00:09:16,680 --> 00:09:18,240
Suffering humiliation,

128
00:09:18,240 --> 00:09:19,570
they dared not speak up.

129
00:09:21,080 --> 00:09:23,120
They started to doubt life,

130
00:09:23,440 --> 00:09:26,240
believing they were just unlucky

131
00:09:26,240 --> 00:09:27,960
to be chosen by the devil.

132
00:09:29,920 --> 00:09:32,120
Until they saw each other,

133
00:09:32,880 --> 00:09:34,280
they finally understood

134
00:09:34,920 --> 00:09:37,000
that in the roulette of fate,

135
00:09:37,640 --> 00:09:41,400
no one is lucky.

136
00:09:43,600 --> 00:09:44,000
Perhaps,

137
00:09:44,000 --> 00:09:47,240
every girl knew what Xu Qiaoyue was going to do.

138
00:09:47,520 --> 00:09:51,050
But they were still willing to hold up an umbrella for Xu Qiaoyue

139
00:09:51,880 --> 00:09:53,680
to shield her from the storm.

140
00:09:57,360 --> 00:10:00,640
The accident was Lighthouse's design.

141
00:10:00,800 --> 00:10:04,040
There's no time. They found me.

142
00:10:04,680 --> 00:10:06,440
I can't leave.

143
00:10:06,440 --> 00:10:10,000
Which will come first, tomorrow or an accident?

144
00:10:18,200 --> 00:10:19,760
Anyway,

145
00:10:19,760 --> 00:10:23,560
celebrating the official establishment of our Accident Investigation Team

146
00:10:23,560 --> 00:10:24,880
is the most important thing.

147
00:10:24,880 --> 00:10:28,080
Let's welcome Mr. Cheng Mo.

148
00:10:28,080 --> 00:10:28,680
Welcome.

149
00:10:28,680 --> 00:10:30,240
Welcome, Mr. Cheng.

150
00:10:30,240 --> 00:10:30,770
Welcome.

151
00:10:31,360 --> 00:10:31,820
Cheers.

152
00:10:31,920 --> 00:10:32,520
Welcome.

153
00:10:32,640 --> 00:10:33,770
Welcome, Mr. Cheng.

154
00:10:36,080 --> 00:10:38,080
Come on, say a few words to everyone.

155
00:10:43,680 --> 00:10:44,400
Thank you.

156
00:10:45,920 --> 00:10:46,920
That's it?

157
00:10:47,800 --> 00:10:48,400
That's it.

158
00:10:49,720 --> 00:10:50,920
Good.

159
00:10:51,800 --> 00:10:52,440
Good.

160
00:10:53,080 --> 00:10:53,800
Well said, Mr. Cheng.

161
00:10:53,800 --> 00:10:54,400
Well said.

162
00:10:55,000 --> 00:10:56,520
After welcoming Mr. Cheng,

163
00:10:56,520 --> 00:10:57,780
let me propose a toast.

164
00:10:58,560 --> 00:10:59,560
This second toast

165
00:11:00,200 --> 00:11:02,080
is to celebrate the Mu Weijie case

166
00:11:02,520 --> 00:11:03,760
being successfully closed.

167
00:11:03,760 --> 00:11:04,880
Although the process was bumpy,

168
00:11:04,880 --> 00:11:07,000
the truth finally came out, right?

169
00:11:07,160 --> 00:11:09,760
In all my years as a police officer,

170
00:11:09,760 --> 00:11:12,160
this is the most beautifully handled case.

171
00:11:12,240 --> 00:11:13,680
Cheers.

172
00:11:13,680 --> 00:11:14,560
Wait.

173
00:11:15,320 --> 00:11:16,760
I also want to say something.

174
00:11:16,760 --> 00:11:17,560
Go ahead.

175
00:11:19,200 --> 00:11:20,080
Here's the thing.

176
00:11:20,080 --> 00:11:21,810
Cheng Mo was amazing this time.

177
00:11:22,000 --> 00:11:23,320
Especially your

178
00:11:23,320 --> 00:11:25,680
deduction of combining five pills into one.

179
00:11:25,680 --> 00:11:27,240
It was a stroke of genius.

180
00:11:28,880 --> 00:11:29,640
But,

181
00:11:29,840 --> 00:11:30,400
Captain,

182
00:11:30,880 --> 00:11:33,520
I actually thought of the same thing as Cheng Mo long ago.

183
00:11:33,520 --> 00:11:34,580
What are you doing?

184
00:11:36,840 --> 00:11:37,760
Come on,

185
00:11:37,760 --> 00:11:39,160
you always talk the most.

186
00:11:46,280 --> 00:11:47,440
In this case,

187
00:11:47,960 --> 00:11:49,360
you are a great hero.

188
00:11:49,440 --> 00:11:49,920
So,

189
00:11:50,720 --> 00:11:51,720
no matter what,

190
00:11:51,720 --> 00:11:53,160
you still need to say a few more words to us.

191
00:11:53,160 --> 00:11:54,400
How can just a 'thank you' be enough?

192
00:11:54,400 --> 00:11:54,920
No way.

193
00:11:54,920 --> 00:11:55,280
Say something.

194
00:11:55,280 --> 00:11:55,880
Share with us.

195
00:11:55,880 --> 00:11:57,120
Actually,

196
00:12:01,680 --> 00:12:03,480
I'm very happy to meet everyone.

197
00:12:04,040 --> 00:12:05,160
Knowing you all

198
00:12:05,840 --> 00:12:07,400
is our destiny.

199
00:12:08,280 --> 00:12:09,160
Of course,

200
00:12:09,720 --> 00:12:11,520
establishing the Accident Investigation Team

201
00:12:11,520 --> 00:12:12,800
for us,

202
00:12:13,040 --> 00:12:14,080
is a mission.

203
00:12:14,560 --> 00:12:15,280
So,

204
00:12:15,520 --> 00:12:16,780
we must uphold justice

205
00:12:17,560 --> 00:12:18,760
and punish the evil.

206
00:12:19,800 --> 00:12:22,880
Let the truth come out in every case,

207
00:12:23,960 --> 00:12:26,200
bring justice to every case,

208
00:12:26,680 --> 00:12:28,760
and to the families and victims.

209
00:12:29,040 --> 00:12:30,000
A fair chance,

210
00:12:31,400 --> 00:12:32,720
with no regrets.

211
00:12:36,760 --> 00:12:37,240
Okay.

212
00:12:37,480 --> 00:12:37,920
Okay.

213
00:12:39,960 --> 00:12:40,600
Okay.
